ness advice  the facilitation of business partnerships  market assessments  the facilitation of new ventures and  governmental and program analysis risk management division prior nm rothschild  sons ltd nm rothschild  sons ltd provides banking and financial services it offers investment and commercial banking treasury merchant banking fund management private banking and trust management services to governments corporations and individuals the company has operations in usa zimbabwe south africa switzerland united arab emirates sweden turkey singapore russia and spain nm rothschild  sons was founded in  and is headquartered in london the united kingdom professional prior jnr ltd boards  committees corporate boards ▾ director tenure unconfirmed j rothschild capital management ltd j rothschild capital management ltd jrcml is the whollyowned investment management subsidiary of rit capital partners plc in the ukestablished in  the firm is based in london and provides investment management services nonprofit boards ▾ member advisory council tenure unconfirmed cornell university  irwin and joan jacobs technion innovation institute the joan  irwin jacobs technioncornell institute embodies the academic partnership between the technion – israel institute of technology and cornell university on the cornell tech campus vice president  director tenure unconfirmed rothschild family foundation member board of trustees tenure unconfirmed yad hanadiv yad hanadiv is dedicated to creating resources for advancing israel as a healthy vibrant democratic society committed to jewish values and equal opportunity for the benefit of all its inhabitants carrying forward the philanthropic tradition of the rothschild familyestablished in its present form in  the foundation’s work has been guided over the years by a distinguished advisory committee other affiliations james rothschild is affiliated with lepe partners llp trigranit development corporation hargreave hale ltd monument capital group ll